Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.58,0:05:18.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偽裝鏡面及第1重力波防護罩被破壞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.63,0:05:20.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對抗措施無效
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.71,0:05:22.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,步行者繼續前進！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.80,0:05:24.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,航向15° 速度20
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.42,0:05:27.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒必要和對方正面衝突
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.05,0:05:28.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法芙娜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.60,0:05:30.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部就緒
