Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.69,0:06:29.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(482,655)}ousia
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.69,0:06:29.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs32\an7}註：原意為「實體」、「本質」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.61,0:06:30.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正直奔彥島
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.49,0:06:32.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,數量和法芙娜隊一樣嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.78,0:06:36.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史彥 放出諾倫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.78,0:06:36.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(725,655)}norn
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.37,0:06:38.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你才剛醒就放沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.87,0:06:42.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,查探對方的想法還是能做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.21,0:06:44.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我也控制不了太多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.85,0:06:54.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,諾倫 展開完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.18,0:06:56.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第3、第4重力波防護罩展開
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.39,0:06:59.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戰場形成完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.52,0:07:04.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法芙娜部隊 出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.28,0:07:17.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,諾倫 開始與烏西亞型交戰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.08,0:07:19.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,距彥島還有5000單位
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.33,0:07:21.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可別輸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.17,0:07:24.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同步完成
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.84,0:07:27.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全體留在原地 可別輕舉妄動
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.51,0:07:31.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 系統是劍司前輩在操縱？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.72,0:07:34.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敵人的統帥就在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.43,0:07:36.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都要活著回去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.35,0:07:38.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰也不能死！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.27,0:07:40.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的想法 太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.69,0:07:45.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,諾倫？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.57,0:07:48.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,替我們承擔了緒戰的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.40,0:07:51.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,究竟是誰在操縱這些遙控機器人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.37,0:08:03.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.83,0:08:05.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們還是擔心自己吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.00,0:08:08.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敵人正在學習島的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.74,0:08:41.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高帕程式 啟動！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.42,0:08:48.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美三香！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.14,0:08:58.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要來比劍術嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.94,0:09:06.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這都行嗎…！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.07,0:09:19.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.04,0:09:29.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這群東西是搶奪武器用的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.42,0:09:32.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,針對各部機體的特性派出的個體嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.26,0:09:35.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,退下 天照 位置變更
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.13,0:09:36.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特性…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.84,0:09:40.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 只要打倒一隻
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.81,0:09:43.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他的就都不成問題了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.40,0:09:55.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.11,0:09:57.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都叫你退下了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.95,0:10:06.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我打的可是SB彈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.95,0:10:06.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(700,655)}small-bore
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.58,0:10:10.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每發的波長都不一樣 為什麼會打不到敵人？
