Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.64,0:10:29.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,月讀命切換到止痛模式
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.23,0:10:31.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解除限定連接
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.16,0:10:47.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美三香！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.25,0:10:51.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.05,0:10:57.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.01,0:10:59.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,預測了我的動作！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.34,0:11:41.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,駕駛艙彈射口被重力波防護罩堵住了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.63,0:11:42.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,駕駛員無法脫離
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.05,0:11:45.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,CDC 暫時解除防護罩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.51,0:11:47.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真壁司令！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.97,0:11:50.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以 史彥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.77,0:11:52.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們是保護龍宮島的戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.40,0:11:56.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要還有力量 就不能退出戰場
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.11,0:11:57.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,力量？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.11,0:12:01.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們還有力量？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.82,0:12:06.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,島…要保護龍宮島
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.00,0:12:12.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要保護乙姬的島！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.69,0:12:36.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mk.Ⅻ 嚴重損毀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.19,0:12:38.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,駕駛員生死未卜！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.90,0:12:41.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,齊格飛系統 無響應！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.24,0:12:48.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要把你…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.08,0:12:51.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要把你幹掉…！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.71,0:12:56.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.52,0:13:16.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第3重力波防護罩 正被敵人的攻擊削弱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.48,0:13:17.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天照 墜落！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.56,0:13:19.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mk.Sein和Mk.Nicht呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.11,0:13:22.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還處於第三啟動階段
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.48,0:13:22.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.99,0:13:25.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍穴 準備打開！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.36,0:13:30.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 現在不能讓一騎和總士戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.33,0:13:32.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法芙娜部隊已經接近全軍覆沒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.33,0:13:36.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,需要戰鬥力來確保區域的分離和撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.71,0:13:39.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們得到的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.55,0:13:42.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,並沒有如此不堪一擊
