Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.06,0:15:31.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是敵人嗎？地點在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.32,0:15:36.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地點是…樞要區域
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.28,0:15:41.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樞要區域？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.07,0:15:46.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站起來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.61,0:15:49.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.42,0:15:52.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把Mk.Ⅲ調出來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.22,0:15:53.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咲良？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.52,0:15:55.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太亂來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.91,0:15:59.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了開發無人機 已經把整個系統重製了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.73,0:16:01.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係！我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.79,0:16:03.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mk.Ⅻ 重新啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.40,0:16:05.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.32,0:16:19.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…為什麼 還活著…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.04,0:16:43.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…怎麼像一騎前輩一樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.88,0:16:51.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我動啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.91,0:17:02.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是 怎麼回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.33,0:17:30.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這武器是從哪來的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.24,0:17:34.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,武器庫裡的武器正在消失
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.79,0:17:36.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有射出的跡象
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.34,0:17:39.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底發生了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.99,0:17:41.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各機的內核…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.82,0:17:43.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,內核正在增殖！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.88,0:17:46.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法芙娜全機 繼續戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.26,0:17:51.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,機庫報告機體內核正在發生未知現象
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.89,0:17:54.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.85,0:17:55.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.00,0:17:57.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是你們所希望的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.58,0:17:59.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將我喚醒的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.80,0:18:02.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為你們而存在的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.25,0:18:08.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安分點 亡靈們！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.37,0:18:15.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我控制這個怪物的力量！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.82,0:18:38.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,終於…把怪物的封印解開了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(OP配樂插入)
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.36,0:19:03.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確認Mk.Nicht與Mk.Sein啟動！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.46,0:19:07.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mk.Sein…醒了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.49,0:19:20.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.04,0:19:29.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mk.Ⅻ 留在原地
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.24,0:19:31.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其餘各機交換位置
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.36,0:19:34.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更換戰鬥對象 互相掩護
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.25,0:19:36.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家一起活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.65,0:19:40.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要保護龍宮島…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.82,0:19:42.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保護乙姬的島！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.75,0:19:49.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要守住！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(OP歌詞插入)
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.79,0:20:10.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太慢了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.11,0:20:31.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將軍了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.14,0:20:43.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,機動手臂上閃耀高帕標誌之時
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.15,0:20:47.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,代代相傳的靈魂正是折不斷的利刃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.19,0:20:52.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超必殺·高帕一閃！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.52,0:21:01.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你漫畫中毒了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.87,0:21:13.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然不太明白
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.09,0:21:18.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過反正像一騎前輩那樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.59,0:21:21.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去做就對了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.40,0:21:38.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.59,0:21:46.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老大來了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.94,0:22:13.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們的願望只有一個
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.88,0:22:16.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是長久的和平
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.50,0:22:21.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 為此我們行使的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.14,0:22:25.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卻總是與和平相去甚遠的力量
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（ED）
